Song - Class in <Unnamed>
The song class is used to initialize a song, whether that be by manually assigning the the artist, song, etc., or by passing in an info String and then parsing it in order to assign the values.
Song(String) - Constructor for class Song
Initializes a song by parsing a string containing the title, artist, and the time of a song with a semicolon and a space using the static delimiter variables and then assigning it
Song(String, String, int[]) - Constructor for class Song
Initializes a song by assigning the title, the artist, and the time of a song, manually
